[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "深水区，地处第一和第二隔离墙之间，此时也雪落不止。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "零区的污染程度并不是线性改变，而是遵循着平方反比定律，靠近尤克特拉希尔时，污染便会指数级增长。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "即使是海姆达尔部队，在没有特殊任务时也不会进入深水区。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "异化人",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "吼……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "两颗子弹干脆利落地结束了游荡的异化人，但这枪响也如黑夜中的火星，顿时引起了其他泰坦和异化人的注意。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "打消了继续潜行的想法，里芙慢慢从掩体后走出。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "从缓冲区到污染区，她已经轻车熟路，几个闪身便绕过了平日里大型敌人出没的地方，一路毫无阻拦地来到了深水区。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可深水区的情况还是远超她的想象——不仅敌人变得更多、更警觉，不断攀升的污染也让她的太阳穴激烈地跳动起来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她会来到这里，只是因为这边是那只海拉败逃的方向。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就在她再次扬起手，准备攻击逐渐靠近的敌人时，一只手轻轻放在了她的肩头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可算追上了啊……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员？！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "来不及解决眼前的敌人，里芙第一反应便是扭头过来，从上到下扫视了我一遍。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "放心，我没受伤。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "见她还是满脸担忧，我抓住她握着枪的手，慢慢转回去，扣下扳机——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "密集的冲锋枪子弹倾泻而出，顿时将敌人一扫而空。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好了，这样就能放心说话了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，你怎么……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我来追那只海拉。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "诶？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我的回答显然超出了里芙的预料，她愣愣地看着我，像是想从我脸上看出几个文字来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不，这太危险……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "经由她自己说出这句话后，我终于忍不住笑了出来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你这不是知道吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "到了这时，里芙终于反应过来我是在揶揄她，那张原本绷得紧紧的脸一下子松了下去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……我还不想回去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "看着面前那张总是冷若冰霜的脸流露出委屈的神色，我不禁在心里摇了摇头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "越是里芙这样坚强的少女，在这种时候就越显得惹人怜爱。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我不是来带你回去的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-1",
        "Flag": "b-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "b-1-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "朝她伸出手",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我们一起冒险吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "什……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没有留给她思考的时间，我已经拉住了她伸出一半的手，快步跑了起来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在追赶她的路上，我已经做出了决定。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "既然不想劝服她，那就……干脆陪她疯一次吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "有了歌唱者的帮助，我们很轻松就找到了那只海拉的位置。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我和里芙躲在一幢大楼的天台上，而海拉此时就在我们正下方。显然，由于之前受到了重创，它正安静地倚坐在楼前。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "周围的泰坦物质不断被吸引过来，又四散成星星点点的小块，填补到它身上的坑坑洼洼里。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这是我第一次近距离观察到泰坦进行自我修复，如果以研究者的视角来看，这个画面大概还算有趣。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "只可惜，我和里芙都不是研究者。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "趁这时候，从后面攻击它的核心，应该就能一击毙命。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但现在它背靠着墙……嗯，得先把它引开才行。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我们是两只循着血腥味追来的狼，三言两语间，便为海拉选好了死法。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所以结论是，我去吸引它的注意，你来了结它。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我们只有两个人，安全第一，别逞强。如果一击没有得手，立刻撤退。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "到那时候，我会拖住它的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "别说傻话。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她总是这样。自己行动时全然不顾危险，而在有人同行时，又会习惯性地做出最坏的打算。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但这一次，我可是坚决得很。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我说了，会陪你冒险的。在确定你撤退以后，我才会撤退。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……我明白了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "为了分析员，我不会失手。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我见里芙收起了眼中的悲观，全身上下开始散发起一股令人生畏的战意。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "对，这个眼神才对，我在心中默念道。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好……上吧。",
        "disable": 0
    }
]